### 3. RSA Key Setup (ทำครั้งเดียว)

```bash
openssl genrsa -out private.pem 2048
openssl rsa -in private.pem -pubout -out public.pem

dotnet user-secrets set "Jwt:PrivateKey" "<base64-private-pem>"
dotnet user-secrets set "Email:Username" "samphan.paw@king-pac.com"
dotnet user-secrets set "Email:Password" "51522515"
```

