### 4. Models & DTOs

#### [NEW] `Models/User.cs` · `Models/Client.cs` · `Models/RefreshToken.cs`
#### [NEW] `Models/AuthDtos.cs`
```
LoginRequest        { Username, Password }
LoginResponse       { AccessToken, ExpiresIn }
RegisterRequest     { Username, Email, Password, ConfirmPassword }
ChangePasswordReq   { CurrentPassword, NewPassword, ConfirmNewPassword }
ForgotPasswordReq   { Email }
ResetPasswordReq    { Token, NewPassword, ConfirmNewPassword }
MeResponse          { Id, Username, Email, Role }
IntrospectRequest   { Token }
IntrospectResponse  { Active, Sub, Username, Email, Role, Exp }
```

---

### 5. Services

#### [NEW] `Services/JwtService.cs`
- RS256 — Private Key จาก User Secrets
- `GenerateAccessToken(User)` → JWT 15 นาที (sub, username, email, role)
- `GenerateRefreshToken()` → 64 bytes random
- `GenerateResetToken()` → 32 bytes hex
- `ValidateToken(token)` → ClaimsPrincipal
- `GetJwks()` → JWKS JSON (Public Key)

#### [NEW] `Services/EmailService.cs`
- SMTP: `mail.king-pac.com:587`
- `SendPasswordResetEmailAsync(to, token, username)`

#### [NEW] `Services/TokenCleanupService.cs`
- Background job ทุก 24 ชม. — ลบ token หมดอายุ/revoked

---

### 6. Controllers

#### [NEW] `Controllers/AuthController.cs`

| Method | Route | Feature | Auth |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | สมัครสมาชิก | Public |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login → JWT + Refresh Cookie | Public |
| POST | `/api/auth/refresh` | Rotate Refresh Token | Cookie |
| POST | `/api/auth/logout` | Revoke + clear cookie | Public |
| GET  | `/api/auth/me` | ข้อมูล user | `[Authorize]` |
| POST | `/api/auth/change-password` | เปลี่ยน password | `[Authorize]` |
| POST | `/api/auth/forgot-password` | ส่ง reset email | Public |
| POST | `/api/auth/reset-password` | Reset ด้วย token | Public |
| POST | `/api/auth/introspect` | ตรวจ JWT แทน API อื่น | Client Auth |

**Cookie:** `HttpOnly=true, Secure=true, SameSite=Strict, Expires=+7days`

#### [NEW] `Controllers/WellKnownController.cs`
- `GET /.well-known/jwks.json` → Public Key

#### [NEW] `Controllers/ClientsController.cs`
- CRUD `/api/clients` — `[Authorize(Role="admin")]`

