### 7. Program.cs

#### [MODIFY] [Program.cs](file:///d:/_dev/_2026_workshop/_claude_api/my-api/Program.cs)
```
AddAuthentication().AddJwtBearer(RS256)
AddAuthorization()  — role-based policy
AddCors()           — multiple origins, AllowCredentials
AddRateLimiter()    — 5 req/min บน /login, /forgot-password
AddScoped<IJwtService, JwtService>()
AddScoped<IEmailService, SmtpEmailService>()
AddHostedService<TokenCleanupService>()

Middleware: UseCors → UseAuthentication → UseAuthorization → UseRateLimiter
```

